### Environment

| | Version |
|---|---|
| `@tanstack/devtools-vite` | `0.7.0` (regression from `0.6.0`) |
| `vite` | `8.0.13` |
| OS | Windows |

### Workaround

Pin back to `@tanstack/devtools-vite@0.6.0`, or wrap the return in a fragment so stripping the devtools node still leaves valid syntax:

